:.START

Dis Toronto closed-end fund cut di yearly dividend on top e class A common to 10 Canadian cents.

Di fund investment na mostly di gold, and silva bullion.

E say di reduced dividend dey reflect low price of precious metal.

George Davies, Central Fund vice president, finance, na im don fall for di fiscal year ending October 31 wey be like one million Canadian dollars (US$85,000.)

Di fund last last, for 1985.

Di new dividend rate na Nov. 15 to take dey mark October 31.

For American Stock Exchange composite trading Friday, Central Fund still dey for $4.6875.

